				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>iz UNK "tu op a hitl, un vets retn dayne kinder." zogt er "ikh vel nisht retn ma- mayne kinder. ikh vel nisht leygn a tsveytn in der erd arayn"</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
